{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium "Business Information & Grievance Officer" section for a luxury Ayurvedic hair wellness brand called Livgenix.
    
    Design Goal:
    Present Livgenix's official business information and grievance redressal details in a clean, trustworthy, and premium way that complies with Indian e-commerce standards.
    
    Layout:
    - Full-width section.
    - Soft cream background (#ECE2CE).
    - Two-column responsive layout.
    - Left column: Business Information.
    - Right column: Grievance Officer.
    - Rounded information cards with generous spacing.
    - Maximum content width: 1400px.
    
    LEFT COLUMN
    
    Small Eyebrow:
    BUSINESS INFORMATION
    
    Heading:
    Registered Business Details
    
    Display the following information inside a premium information card:
    
    • Registered Company Name
    • Registered Office Address
    • Customer Support Email
    • Customer Support Phone
    • GST Number
    • CIN (Optional)
    • FSSAI License Number (Optional)
    
    Each item should have a clean minimalist line icon.
    
    RIGHT COLUMN
    
    Small Eyebrow:
    GRIEVANCE REDRESSAL
    
    Heading:
    Need Additional Assistance?
    
    Display a premium contact card containing:
    
    • Grievance Officer Name
    • Designation
    • Email Address
    • Phone Number
    • Office Address
    • Response Timeline
      (Example: We aim to respond within 48 business hours.)
    
    Below the information display a subtle note:
    
    "If your concern remains unresolved through our customer support team, our Grievance Officer will ensure your issue receives prompt attention in accordance with applicable consumer protection guidelines."
    
    Design Style:
    - Luxury editorial design inspired by premium wellness brands.
    - Rounded cards (24px radius).
    - Soft borders.
    - White cards on cream background.
    - No gradients.
    - No heavy shadows.
    - Premium typography.
    - Plenty of whitespace.
    - Simple monochrome line icons.
    - Smooth fade-up animation.
    
    Color Palette:
    Background: #ECE2CE
    Cards: White
    Heading: #2F3324
    Accent: #BE9A5C
    Body Text: #6B705C
    Borders: #DDD6C4
    
    The overall feeling should communicate transparency, trust, professionalism, and customer-first service rather than appearing overly corporate.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-business-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_mobile }}px 20px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-business-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_desktop }}px 40px;
    }
  }

  .ai-business-info-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-business-info-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 990px) {
    .ai-business-info-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }
  }

  .ai-business-info-column-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: ai-business-info-fade-up-{{ ai_gen_id }} 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .ai-business-info-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }

  @keyframes ai-business-info-fade-up-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .ai-business-info-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_size }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .ai-business-info-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-business-info-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-business-info-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-business-info-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 40px 32px;
    }
  }

  .ai-business-info-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ai-business-info-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .ai-business-info-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .ai-business-info-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    stroke: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .ai-business-info-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .ai-business-info-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: {{ block.settings.label_color }};
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .ai-business-info-value-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.text_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-business-info-note-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.note_background }};
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.note_text_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .ai-business-info-timeline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding: 16px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.timeline_background }};
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.note_text_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }
{% endstyle %}

